<br>
1.  Anti-Summoning Spell:  I think the name speaks for itself.  It would really help us get in groups because no one likes to get summoned.<br>
<br>
2.  Anti-Gate spell:  Again name speaks for itself.  We cast this spell on the target on it would anchor it down.<br>
<br>
3.  The last idea i thought up would actually make familiars useful.  Instead of it just buffing us it would be a group buff.<br>
<br>
